---
import { Image } from "@astrojs/image/components";
import heroImage from "assets/hero-pt.jpg";


---
<div class="my-20">
  <div class="flex items-start space-y-8 lg:space-y-0 ">
    <div class="w-full xl:w-2/3 space-y-2  lg:pr-8">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight  mb-8">The strength to <span class="italic text-slate-600">change oneself</span> is the strongest act of all.</h2>
        <p>Investing in personal growth can lead to transformative changes in various aspects of your life. Whether you are seeking to enhance your relationships, boost your self-confidence, manage stress, or discover your life's purpose, taking proactive steps towards personal development is key. Here are some ways you can embark on a journey of self-improvement:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 list-decimal list-inside text-black py-4">
          <li>Set meaningful goals that align with your values and aspirations.</li>
          <li>Cultivate positive habits and practice self-discipline.</li>
          <li>Expand your knowledge and skills through continuous learning.</li>
          <li>Embrace challenges and step out of your comfort zone to foster personal growth.</li>
          <li>Build a support network of like-minded individuals who inspire and motivate you.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Remember, personal growth is a lifelong process that requires commitment and perseverance. It's never too late to embark on this transformative journey. Start investing in your personal growth today and unlock a life filled with happiness, fulfillment, and purpose.</p>
        <p class="pt-4"><a href="#" class="font-semibold hover:underline">Contact us</a> now to explore how our coaching and therapy services can support your personal growth and help you achieve your goals.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center xl:w-1/3">
      <div class="hidden xl:block max-w-xs rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <Image
            src={heroImage}
            alt="Astronaut on moon"
            loading="lazy"
            class="object-cover"

          />
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>